    {
      "text": "The second hamster breeding simulation game. In addition to the familiar \"Shigecchi\", cute new characters are appearing one after another. A new mini-game has been added to the new story, and it is full of fun and cuteness. Comes with a mascot doll as a first-time limited benefit.",
